## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/releasemodemodelrunner">ReleaseModeModelRunner</a> - production mode implementation of the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mlmodelrunner">MLModelRunner</a>.

It uses an AOT-compiled SavedModel for efficient execution.
